				<section>
				  <h4>The e-learning platform we are developing</h4>
				  <img style="border:0px" height="60px" src="assets/akademix-logo-svart.png">
				  <br><br>
				  <ul>
				    <li>Based on WeBWorK and Open EdX</li>
				    <li> Cloud-based and scalable (Amazon AWS)</li>
				    <li class="fragment grow"> Cross-institutional</li>
				  </ul>
				  <br><br>
				  <a href="http://beta.akademix.no">beta.akademix.no</a>
				</section>
				</section>

				<section>
				<section>
				  <p> Long term ambition: </p>
				  <span style="color: blue; font-size:110%;"> Change the way we teach mathematics at HiB</span><br><br>
				  <div class="fragment">
				  <p> Courses consisting of three (interconnected) parts:</p>
				  <p>
				    <ul>
				      <li> Exercise sessions supported by video material </li>
				      <li> Computer labs </li>
				      <li> Overview lectures focusing on ideas, concepts and applications </li>
				    </ul>
				  </p>

				  <img height="150px" src="assets/Manipulation.jpg">&nbsp;&nbsp;<img height="150px" src="assets/hackaton.jpg">&nbsp;&nbsp;<img height="150px" src="assets/Feynman.jpg">
				  </div>
				</section>

				<section>
				  <img height="150px" src="assets/Manipulation.jpg">&nbsp;&nbsp;<img height="150px" src="assets/hackaton.jpg">&nbsp;&nbsp;<img height="150px" src="assets/Feynman.jpg">
				  <br><br><br>
				  Constructivism + Instructivism<br><br>
				  Sage on the stage + Guide on the side
				  <br><br><br>
				  <div class="fragment">
				    <b>Is this a shared vision?</b>
